samo kliknite na link <a href="%s">Instaliraj teme</a>.','You only have one theme enabled for this site right now. Visit the Network Admin to <a href="%1$s">enable</a> or <a href="%2$s">install</a> more themes.'=>'Trenutno imate samo jednu omogućenu temu na ovoj stranici. Posjetite mrežnu administraciju da <a href="%1$s">omogućite</a> ili <a href="%2$s">instalirate</a> više tema.','You only have one theme enabled for this site right now. Visit the Network Admin to <a href="%s">enable</a> more themes.'=>'Trenutno imate samo jednu omogućenu temu na ovoj stranici. Posjetite mrežnu administraciju da <a href="%s">omogućite</a> više tema.','Retro (Generated)'=>'Retro (Generisano)','Sample Page'=>'Probna stranica','sample-page'=>'probna stranica','The boxes on your Dashboard screen are:'=>'Okviri na vašoj kontrolnoj ploči su:','If you want to make changes but do not want them to be overwritten when the plugin is updated, you may be ready to think about writing your own plugin. For information on how to edit plugins, write your own from scratch, or just better understand their anatomy, check out the links below.'=>'Ako želite napraviti izmjene ali ne želite da one prebrišu vaše postavke kada je plugin aktiviran, razmislite o pisanju vašeg vlastitog plugina. Za informacije o uređivanju plugina, pisanju plugina "od nule" ili jednostavno boljeg razumijevanja njihove anatomije, pogledajte linkove ispod.','Any edits to files from this screen will be reflected on all sites in the network.'=>'Bilo kakva uređivanja fajlova na ovoj stranici će se reflektovati na sve stranice u mreži.','Default Post Format'=>'Osnovi format članka','This plugin may be active on other sites in the network.'=>'Ovaj plugin bi mogao biti aktivan na drugim stranicama u mreži.','%s Page Template'=>'%s predložak stranice','paging%1$s of %2$s'=>'%1$s od %2$s','Collapse menu'=>'Zatvori meni','You are using an insecure browser!'=>'Koristite nesiguran browser!','Your browser is out of date!'=>'Vaš browser je zastario!','All Comments'=>'Svi komentari','Translate this to be the equivalent of English Translators in your language for the credits page Translators sectionTranslators'=>'Prevodioci za bosanski jezik','Available Tools'=>'Dostupni alati','Network Setup'=>'Instalacija mreže','The uploaded file exceeds the %s directive that was specified in the HTML form.'=>'Dodani fajl je veći od %s direktive zadane u HTML obrascu.','You can find additional themes for your site by using the Theme Browser/Installer on this screen, which will display themes from the <a href="%s">WordPress Theme Directory</a>. These themes are designed and developed by third parties, are available free of charge, and are compatible with the license WordPress uses.'=>'Dodatne teme za vašu stranicu možete pronaći pomoću instalacije tema na ovom ekranu čime ćete prikazati teme iz <a href="%s">WordPress.org direktorija</a>. Ove teme nije razvio tim zadužen za razvoj WordPressa, ali su sve teme kompatibilne sa licencom koju koristi WordPress.','theme nameName'=>'Naziv','meta nameName'=>'Naziv','There are some invalid menu items. Please check or delete them.'=>'Neke stavke u meniju su neispravne. Molimo vas da ih provjerite ili obrišite.','It looks like you\'re using an insecure version of %s. Using an outdated browser makes your computer unsafe. For the best WordPress experience, please update your browser.'=>'Izgleda da koristite nesigurnu verziju programa %s. Korištenjem zastarjele verzije ugrožavate sigurnost vašeg računara. Za najbolje WordPress iskustvo, molimo vas da nadogradite vaš browser.','It looks like you\'re using an old version of %s. For the best WordPress experience, please update your browser.'=>'Izgleda da koristite staru verziju programa %s. Za najbolje WordPress iskustvo, molimo vas da ažurirate vaš browser. ','If you would like to see more plugins to choose from, click on the &#8220;Add New&#8221; button and you will be able to browse or search for additional plugins from the <a href="%s">WordPress Plugin Directory</a>. Plugins in the WordPress Plugin Directory are designed and developed by third parties, and are compatible with the license WordPress uses. Oh, and they&#8217;re free!'=>'Ako želite vidjeti još tema, kliknite na tab &#8220;Instaliraj teme&#8221; i moći ćete pretraživati dodatne teme iz <a href="%s">WordPress.org direktorija</a>. Ove teme nije razvio tim zadužen za razvoj WordPressa, ali su sve teme kompatibilne sa licencom koju koristi WordPress. I da, besplatne su!','Featured Image Header'=>'Zaglavlje istaknute slike','Featured Images'=>'Istaknute slike','Full Width Template'=>'Predložak pune širine','Post Formats'=>'Formati članaka','Hi,
