emu. Osnovne teme WordPress koristi automatski u slučaju da se desi neka greška sa vašom temom.','Required and recommended modules are installed'=>'Potrebni i preporučeni moduli su instalirani','Error'=>'Greška','The required module, %s, is not installed, or has been disabled.'=>'Neophodni modul %s nije instaliran ili je onemogućen.','The optional module, %s, is not installed, or has been disabled.'=>'Dodatni modul %s nije instaliran ili je onemogućen.','One or more recommended modules are missing'=>'Nedostaje jedan ili više preporučenih modula','One or more required modules are missing'=>'Jedan ili više potrebnih modula nedostaje','SQL server is up to date'=>'SQL server je ažuriran','Outdated SQL server'=>'Zastarjeli SQL server','For optimal performance and security reasons, you should consider running %1$s version %2$s or higher. Contact your web hosting company to correct this.'=>'Zbog optimalnih performansi i sigurnosnih razloga, preporučujemo vam korištenje %1$s verzije %2$s ili novije. Kontaktirajte vašu hosting kompaniju radi promjene.','Severely outdated SQL server'=>'Veoma zastario SQL server','WordPress requires %1$s version %2$s or higher. Contact your web hosting company to correct this.'=>'WordPress zahtjeva  %1$s verziju %2$s ili noviju. Kontaktirajte vašu hosting kompaniju radi promjene.','UTF8MB4 is supported'=>'UTF8MB4 je podržan','utf8mb4 requires a MySQL update'=>'utf8mb4 zahtjeva ažuriranje MySQL','Your MySQL version supports utf8mb4.'=>'Vaša MySQL verzija podržava utf8mb4.','utf8mb4 requires a MariaDB update'=>'utf8mb4 zahtjeva ažuriranje MariaDB','Your MariaDB version supports utf8mb4.'=>'Vaša MariaDB verzija podržava utf8mb4.','utf8mb4 requires a newer client library'=>'utf8mb4 zahtjeva noviju verziju klijentske biblioteke','Can communicate with WordPress.org'=>'Moguće je kontatirati WordPress.org','Communicating with the WordPress servers is used to check for new versions, and to both install and update WordPress core, themes or plugins.'=>'K